'''Broken Mirror''' ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse muri 2014 ikozwe na  Media 5 Studio Productions<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/broken_mirrors</ref>. James Gardiner, Fred Amugi, Jackie Appiah, Roselyn Ngissah, Mikki Osei Berko, Victoria Lebene Mekpah na Jasmine Baroudi ni abakinnyi bingenzi<ref>https://www.menemshafilms.com/broken-mirrors</ref>. Yanditswe na Pappa Deric kandi yakozwe na David Owusu hamwe na Mikki Osei Berko nk'umuyobozi. Ninkuru yumugore uhinda umushyitsi mugihe amahirwe y'umukunzi we ahindutse neza, nyuma yo kumuhagararaho mubihe bikomeye<ref>https://redcarpetcrash.com/movie-review-broken-mirrors/</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Thompson yakinnye na James Gardiner, ni umunyeshuri urangije kaminuza udafite akazi ufata ububaji kugira ngo abeho<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/527611-broken-mirror</ref>. Umukunzi we Priscilla ( Jackie Appiah ) yamuhaye inkunga y'amarangamutima ndetse n'amafaranga<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/527611-broken-mirror</ref>. Priscilla udakize kandi akora akazi ko kudoda, ahora ashimishwa na bagenzi be Evelyn (Roselyn Ngissah) na Angela (Victoria Lebene Mekpah) kubera urukundo rwe no gushyigikira byimazeyo Thompson<ref>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com/broken-mirror/</ref>. Kumwizera kumutsindira mugihe cyImana birakomeye kandi arabikora mugihe cy'umwaka.<ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/final-broken-mirror/oclc/905919617</ref>

Barashyingirwa, barishima kandi bategereje umwana wabo wambere, mugihe Thompson yakiriye amashusho yerekana Priscilla nundi mugabo<ref>https://www.bostonherald.com/2014/04/10/broken-mirror-horror-tale-oculus-shows-cracks/</ref>. Ibi bimuha kumva ko ariganya kandi biganisha ku gusenyuka. Evelyn amenyesha umukunzi we Priscilla mugihe runaka. Hari ukuntu yemera ko Priscilla yamwibye kandi niwe uri ku mashusho hamwe na we<ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2014/10/broken-mirror.html</ref>.

